s aum total includes additional strategies multiasset includes us billion allocated to external managers and us billion allocated to other pinebridge strategies pinebridge is majorityowned by a subsidiary of pacific century group pcg an asiabased private investment group pinebridge employees have a meaningful share in the success of pinebridge through equity ownership and other rights to profits of the business overview leadership senior leadership board of directors media relations in the news press releases office locations closex this website uses cookies to ensure you get the best experience on our website pinebridge investments stronger growth on the horizon markus schomer cfa chief global economist discusses surprises risks and what to expect in markets this year – and beyond closex this website uses cookies to ensure you get the best experience on our website pinebridge office locations  pinebridge investments office locations global headquarters   park avenue th floor new york ny  tel     australia melbourne level   collins street melbourne vic  australia tel     view funds chile santiago el regidor  piso  las condes santiago chile tel    hong kong hong kong level  three pacific place  queens road east hong kong island tel    india mumbai unit no tower b peninsula business park ganpatrao kadam marg lower parel mumbai   maharashtra ireland dublin th floor the observatory building  sir john rogersons quaydublin ireland japan tokyo ja building  otemachi chome chiyodaku tokyo  japan tel     korea seoul level  seoul finance centre sejongdaerojunggu seoul korea  tel     malaysia kuala lumpur suite  level  pavilion kl  jalan bukit bintang  kuala lumpur tel    mexico mexico city blvd manuel a camacho  col lomas de chapultepec méxico dftel     singapore singapore  robinson road aia tower  singapore  central singapore tel    south africa cape town level  willowbridge centre  carl cronje drive tyger valley  south africa main     taiwan kaohsiung rm a f no siwei rd rd l